title: TTC Extra: Pope Francis Meets Kim Davis To The Contrary
text: Pope Francis met with Kim Davis, the Kentucky clerk jailed for refusing to issue marriage licenses to same sex couples. He reportedly told her to "stay strong" but the Vatican says the meeting does not mean he supports her position fully. PANEL: Del Eleanor Holmes Norton, Linda Chavez, Debra Carnahan, Cari Dominguez
